{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"blur","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>blur</code>&nbsp;이벤트는 엘리먼트의 포커스가 해제되었을때 발생합니다. 이 이벤트와&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusout_event\">focusout</a></code>&nbsp;이벤트의 가장 다른점은&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusout_event\">focusout</a></code>&nbsp;은 이벤트 버블링이 발생합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_info","title":"General info","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"specification\">Specification</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events/#event-type-blur\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM L3</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FocusEvent\"><code>FocusEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Element</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"default_action\">Default Action</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">None.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p>이 이벤트가 처리될때 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Document/activeElement\"><code>Document.activeElement</code></a>의 값이 브라우저마다 다릅니다&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=452307\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;452307</a>): IE10은 이 값을 포커스가 옮겨가는 엘리먼트에 추가하지만, 파이어폭스와 크롬은 도큐먼트의 <code>body</code>에 추가합니다.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>Event target (DOM element)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>relatedTarget</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> (DOM element)</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"이벤트_위임","title":"이벤트 위임","isH3":false,"content":"<p>이 이벤트에 이벤트 위임을 적용하는 방법은 두가지가 있습니다&nbsp;: 브라우저가 지원한다면&nbsp;<code>focusout</code>&nbsp;이벤트를 사용하거나,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\">addEventListener</a></code>의 \"useCapture\" 파라미터를 <code>true</code>로 설정하세요:</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_content","title":"HTML Content","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html; notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text input<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript_content","title":"JavaScript Content","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> form <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"form\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nform<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"focus\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pink\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nform<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blur\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"JavaScript Content\" id=\"frame_event_delegation\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event/_sample_.event_delegation.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.blur_event","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_events","title":"Related Events","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">focus (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\" title=\"/ko/docs/Web/Reference/Events/blur\">blur</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusin_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">focusin (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusout_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">focusout (en-US)</a></code></li